#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:179
msgid "About"
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:181
msgid ""
"\n"
"    I built Wasted Sun on my own time, because watching good solar go to "
"waste is maddening—and I’d\n"
"    rather show the numbers than swallow them. It is not an official "
"Octopus Energy product, site, or comms.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:187
msgid ""
"\n"
"    I care fiercely about this in part because of my day job as Head of "
"Technology at Octopus Energy Spain—\n"
"    but unless I say otherwise, every sharp word and chart choice here is"
" mine, not my employer’s.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:195
msgid ""
"\n"
"  Figures are derived from Red Eléctrica de España data and processed "
"independently for this site;\n"
"  they are not official REE publications or government statistics.\n"
"  "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:201
